{"tid":1584184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"脫氧劑當紫菜粉食 淘寶賣家:食少少無事既","createTime":"2019-09-21T03:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T00:40:03.000Z","uid":174013,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a39db71edcc51425910037451116765f300aff94","tid":1584184,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"【轉帖】喺FB見到,笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係痴x線。。。。嬲到癲。。。。。<br />\n點解食落肚既野可以咁兒戲。。。。。<br />\n我原本以為類似係紫菜粉既物體，因為每粒都係好均勻，<br />\n食多幾粒覺得怪怪地，好似食沙咁，再睇下入面，<br />\n見到個脫氧劑爛左。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n即刻影比個客服睇，佢居然覺得係好平常既事，話食少少無事。。。淨係話退返呢包錢比我。。。<br />\n<br />\n依家都唔知點算，想請教下大家係咪真係無事的。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n因為之前成日見到谷友淘飲品/乳酪，所以對淘食物放下左戒心，希望大家之後可以參考一下我個case，以後盡量唔好淘食落肚既野了😥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69984274_2847326925295226_6631953375069995008_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQlCaEfO3V3T4G607mi8eTwC2wDpCVt-hDcO87XCEUdJRNM6k18MpO3Sj-FyBXcxnK0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg9-1.fna&amp;oh=154cf0556c93a5f6a8a974c40aa15ffb&amp;oe=5DF94E8F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69984274_2847326925295226_6631953375069995008_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQlCaEfO3V3T4G607mi8eTwC2wDpCVt-hDcO87XCEUdJRNM6k18MpO3Sj-FyBXcxnK0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg9-1.fna%26oh%3D154cf0556c93a5f6a8a974c40aa15ffb%26oe%3D5DF94E8F&h=bc9e1209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69899744_2847327038628548_8465304300451528704_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkX_O-Ikb-_XKb2ufSd8X0srxcF3pb2-GrmJ2Q25qj2_a20bwm02y09eYDZdTLVaVk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg9-1.fna&amp;oh=803f6e6246d9e90b580011a0c5159bb5&amp;oe=5E3CFF69\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69899744_2847327038628548_8465304300451528704_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkX_O-Ikb-_XKb2ufSd8X0srxcF3pb2-GrmJ2Q25qj